[{"c":"<p>Every promise in the Book is mine,</p><p>Every chapter, every verse, every line,</p><p>All the blessings of His love Divine,</p><p>Every promise in the Book is mine.</p>"},{"c":"<p>Setswana</p>"},{"c":"<p>Ditsholofetso tsotlhe ke tsa me,</p><p>Dikgaolo ditemana le ditsela,</p><p>Ditshegofatso tsa lorato la gagwe,</p><p>Ditsholofetso tsotlhe ke tsa me.</p>"},{"c":"<p>Telugu</p>"},{"c":"<p>grandha vaagdhaanambhu lanni naavi</p><p>prati adhyambhu varusa vachanamu</p><p>tana divya prEma vaagdhaanambhulu</p><p>grandha vaagdhaanambhu lanni naavi.</p>"},{"c":"<p>Hindi</p>"},{"c":"<p>har ek vaayada mere lie hai,</p><p>har ek baab, har ek aayat, har ek laeen,</p><p>us ke pyaar kee saaree barakaten,</p><p>har ek vaayada mere lie hai</p>"}]